parameters:
Fuhahahaha! Welcome, Resistance boy, you've really
moved me by coming here all alone.
President! Where the hell is Esuka!

Isn't she right in front of you? The Bio Chimera.
A touching collaboration of two weapons, the
cyborg sister and the modified soldier sister.

My sister... could it be... Esuka's sister is also
here...?

Indeed. However, due to the side effects of the
fusion, they've turned into such a monster,
fuhahahaha.

Esuka! Can you hear me, Esuka! It's me! Please, I
beg you, respond.

Fuhahahaha! Well then, I suppose I'll just sit
back and enjoy the show.

...As expected of the professor, you're doing a
good job...!
Stay back, Shuu! Mikoto... I'm sorry...!
It's no use... I can't do anything about it...

Shuu... Thank you, leave the rest to me and step
back...! Mikoto... You're going to have to put up
with my selfishness...

Esuka...? What on earth are you... Don't tell
me... Self-destruction...?

President! It's terrible! The United Nations army
is attacking!

It seems that due to the video of the auction,
international public opinion has united against
the empire.

Grr... There's no way they can keep up this united
front forever. No choice! We'll have to retreat
back to our homeland for now!
No, Esuka! Your body isn't ready to move yet...!
But... because of him...! It's all his fault...!

Right now, we just need to focus on surviving
this...!

is attacking!

It seems that the international public opinion has

auction.
